snippet.title: Trying to find trash games Part 1: Rosso Rabbit (No Commentary)
snippet.description: So this is a new thing I'm trying to do finding trash games for PC only. So these controls with arrow up and down keys and to turn left and right  it moves with the mouse the graphics are pretty good for what i'm doing. The game feels like a mobile game... As you can tell I raged halfway through so yeah
